F-35 or Su-57 - What Does India Need? | Wargaming by GD Bakshi

In this edition of 'Wargaming  By GD Bakshi', Retired major general talks about India’s defence needs. He analyses what will be better for India F-35 or Su-57 fighter jets. 
He also talks about Trump’s F-35 offer to India and what it really means. He compares and contrasts the cost, features, efficiency of the fighter jets and the timeline of procurement. He also talks about India’s AMCA project.
Watch the video for details.
